    dct:title "DWUG German (Diachronic Word Usage Graphs, Schlechtweg et al.)"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Benchmark (gold human-annotated lexical semantic change). Ingested as detection-grade backbone: derived target-word + gold graded-change only, no raw usage graphs, no causal claim (ADR 0004)."@en ;
